<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-18 10:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5344 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-TECH-STARTUP-BOS &LR;      07-18 0763
