<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PSYCHOLOGY-LECRONE-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Personality disorder calls for psychotherapy
 &HT;    By Hap LeCrone
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
