<P>
   INTEL-EARNINGS (Undated) _ Intel will report earnings Tuesday
after the stock market closes. The consensus forecast is 98 cents a
share, including a one-time gain and a one-time charge but not
accounting for the company's planned 2-for-1 stock split. By
Barnaby J. Feder.
</P>
<P>
   GM-EARNINGS (Detroit) _ General Motors said its earnings rose 1
percent in the second-quarter, higher than estimates, on demand for
high-profit sport-utility vehicles. By Keith Bradsher.
</P>
<P>
