   One of Boston's newest hotels, the Seaport, is offering summer
packages beginning at $169 a night. The hotel is also offering
guests a free one-hour harbor cruise on Sunday mornings. Among
packages is one for $299 that includes a Spirit of Boston dinner
cruise (it leaves across the street from the hotel), a hotel stay,
free parking, and a buffet breakfast for two. For information, call
877-SEAPORT.
</P>
<P>
   Travelers staying at Holiday Inns nationwide and using their
Visa card receive a free value book with hundreds of dollars worth
of retail offers, from discounted fares on US Airways to free
