and Eat Free deal. For information, call 800-272-9273.
</P>
<P>
   The Sheraton Boston Hotel is featuring a family Ducky Package at
$179 a night on weekends. The package includes accommodations, a
connecting room at a 50 percent discount, free meals for those
under 12, a fun pack with games and prizes, bath and bedtime duck
toys for youngsters, and a visit from Tuck the Duck, the hotel's
quacky mascot who offers bedtime stories along with milk and
