guy who's going to last.
</P>
<P>
   ``I am confident, and I say this as humbly as possible, talent
prevails in the end,'' he says. ``I know what I can do and I'm
confident that I can make a long career out of this. There is this
whole business side of it _ you can make a bad movie, things can
happen, and suddenly you're not the flavor of the month anymore,
