</P>
<P>
   TV_Network share 0719 -- 1 x 7 -- Weekly graphic
</P>
<P>
   Weekly ratings chart foe the major newtorks.
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL
</P>
<P>
   WHATSDOING_Edinburgh, Scotland -- 2 x 4 -- travel feature
</P>
<P>
   Locator map
</P>
<P>
   VITAL STATS_Edinburgh, Scotland  -- 1 x 5 -- travel feature
</P>
<P>
   Helpful travel statistics on Philidelphia
