<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-18 20:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5991 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-ECON-REPORT-ART-NYT &LR;      07-18 1181
