</P>
<P>
   By Regina Hackett. (Story has moved in the ``e'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   TV-TOUR-URINALS (Pasadena, Calif.) _ Is there honor among TV
critics? Not in the men's room. Several promotional posters placed
above urinals in a Ritz-Carlton hotel restroom in Pasadena went
missing soon after they were installed to tie in with a news
conference on ABC's fall marketing campaign.
</P>
<P>
   By John Levesque. (Story has moved in the ``e'' category.)
</P>
