<HEADLINE>
AIR-TRAFFIC SYSTEM APPROACHED GRIDLOCK, WITH DELAYS OF UP TO 8
HOURS 
</HEADLINE>
  (duplication notice: also sent with `f' code) 
 By JOE SHARKEY   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
